title: Gucci Mane & Young Thug - The Purple Album [2014] [Album]
description:
Gucci Mane has announced a new series of albums which will feature contributions from Migos, Young Thug, and Peewee Longway.

Last summer, Gucci Mane hit us with a trilogy of albums in one day, dropping the World War 3 series, based on three of his greatest vices; Gas, Molly, and Lean. Ironically, the drank-inspired project was easily the strongest of the series, showcasing the new wave of his carefully built Brick Squad crew, the potential of which only becoming clear to most after Wop's most recent arrest.

The new trilogy, titled World War 3D, will feature releases from Migos, Young Thug, and Peewee Longway. With the projects titled The Green Album, The Purple Album, and The White Album respectively
